Auth APIs
Register User
URI: /api/auth/register
Method: POST
Body:
fullName
email
password
address (optional)
Login User
URI: /api/auth/login
Method: POST
Body:
email
password
Cart APIs
Add Item to Cart
URI: /api/cart
Method: POST
Body:
productId
quantity
Get Cart Items
URI: /api/cart
Method: GET
Body: None
Favorite APIs
Add Item to Favorites
URI: /api/favorite
Method: POST
Body:
productId
Get Favorite Items
URI: /api/favorite
Method: GET
Body: None
Order APIs
Create New Order (Checkout)
URI: /api/order/checkout
Method: POST
Body:
totalPrice
status (optional)
Get Order Details
URI: /api/order/:orderId
Method: GET
Body: None
Get All Orders (for authenticated users)
URI: /api/order
Method: GET
Body: None
Update Order Status (for admin)
URI: /api/order/:orderId
Method: PUT
Body:
status
Product APIs
Get All Products
URI: /api/products
Method: GET
Body: None
Get Product Details
URI: /api/product/:productId
Method: GET
Body: None
Create New Product (for admin)
URI: /api/product
Method: POST
Body:
title
description
price
imageUrl
Update Product Details (for admin)
URI: /api/product/:productId
Method: PUT
Body:
title (optional)
description (optional)
price (optional)
imageUrl (optional)
Delete Product (for admin)
URI: /api/product/:productId
Method: DELETE
Body: None
Logout API (/api/auth/logout)
Remove Item from Cart API (/api/cart/:productId)
Update Cart Item Quantity API (/api/cart/:productId)
Remove Item from Favorites API (/api/favorite/:productId)
Get All Orders API for admin (/api/orders)

